%% Diagram: Thread Pool Lifecycle (uv_queue_work)
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Caller on main thread
    participant EL as Event Loop
    participant Queue as Work Queue
    participant W as Worker Thread
    participant CB as after_work_cb on main thread
    App->>EL: call uv_queue_work with req and callbacks
    EL->>Queue: enqueue uv_work_t
    Note over EL: Pool initialised lazily on first queued work
    Queue->>W: dequeue, next idle worker
    activate W
    W->>W: run work_cb, blocking or CPU-bound
    Note over W: req->data carries context across threads
    W-->>EL: signal completion via async wakeup
    deactivate W
    EL->>CB: schedule after_work_cb on next iteration
    activate CB
    CB->>CB: read req->data, free resources
    deactivate CB
    Note over App,CB: uv_cancel cancels only queued, not running, work
